data.description: Here is your chance to Own an amazing home that helps pay the Electrical Bills with a SOLAR POWER of 3.8 kW/hr! This immaculate house offers 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, soaring vaulted ceilings, and a split bedroom design that provides plenty of privacy. From the front door, the hallway leads to the kitchen, dining and living room. The kitchen boasts staggered cabinetry, GE appliances, a food pantry, and a generous-sized kitchen island that doubles as a breakfast bar. 18"x18" tile flooring throughout the living area except for bedrooms. Both bathrooms were upgraded with glass sliding doors. The property includes a washer and dryer and some furniture available upon request. Enjoy Florida sunsets from your fully fenced backyard with lush greenery including multiple fruit trees. HOA fee includes LAWN maintenance. The property offers a structural home warranty from the builder. Vista Palms has a variety of wonderful amenities including a swimming pool, splash pad area, fitness center, playground, etc. You will make use of a community clubhouse with a large gathering area with a kitchen and pool table. Contact the agent for more information and numbers for the solar power transfer.
